Action:
Start a level (Read below)
Dodge enemies, jumping, moving left and right, sometimes up and down, parrying
Shoot enemies, use the attack key to lower your enemies' health, parrying fills up super attack meter for more damage
Complete bosses, by both attacking and dodging the boss, you'll eventually whittle the boss's health down.
Reward:
Marks level as complete
Marks up total level score
Get coins for collectibles
Progression:
Unlock new levels
Unlock new abilities
Unlock collectibles
Long Term Progression: Complete story (repay your debt to the devil)
